These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, davidoff
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: november, april
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cycling, surfing
There 2 different types of food: avocado, cucumber
1. the person eating cucumber is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3
2. the davidoff-smoker is in an even position##4
3. the person who's birthday is in april is the prince-smoker##1
4. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the person eating avocado##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Cigar      | prince  | davidoff   |
| Birthday   | april     | november   |
| Sport         | surfing | cycling |
| Food     | avocado | cucumber    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  dancer, bartender
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: disco, indie
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, march
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, tram
1. the person who's birthday is in march is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of disco is the person driving the tram##1
3. the bartender is on the right of the fan of indie##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Job          | dancer     | bartender |
| Music-Genre   | indie | disco  |
| Birthday           | march         | august     |
| Transport     | motorbike   | tram    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, soy-milk
City: nizza, marseilles
2 different games are played: bridge, go
There are 2 different nationalities: italian, american
1. the american is on the left or right of the person traveling to marseilles##3
2. the person playing go is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Beverage    | soy-milk     | hot-chocolate |
| City         | marseilles | nizza    |
| Game         | bridge         | go        |
| Nationality   | italian         | american    |

