There 2 different types of food: strawberry, zucchini
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, pall-mall
2 different games are played: bridge, whist
1. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
2. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
3. the person playing whist is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Pet      | guinea-pig     | bird |
| Food          | zucchini   | strawberry  |
| Cigar         | blend | pall-mall     |
| Game   | bridge  | whist         |

