.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-6::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  coach, electrician
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: tulip, balloon-flower
There are 2 different favourite beverages: water, fanta
2 different games are played: canasta, scrabble
1. the person playing scrabble is in an even position##4
2. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the far left or far right##3
3. the electrician is the person who growstulip##1
4. the person drinking water is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Job           | electrician | coach    |
| Flower   | tulip       | balloon-flower |
| Beverage           | water         | fanta    |
| Game         | canasta    | scrabble   |

