The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: mystery, scientific
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, van
The people have 2 different hobbies: hiking, fishing
1. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
3. the bongani-smoker is in an even position##4
4. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |        2        |
| Cigar           | alhambra | bongani |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery    | scientific      |
| Transport           | airplane      | van          |
| Hobby         | fishing | hiking       |

