.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-20::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: trance, house
There are 2 different nationalities: german, russian
2 different pets are kept: frog, goat
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: climbing, basketball
1. the russian is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
2. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
3. the person who's sport is climbing is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |    2     |
| Music-Genre    | trance | house    |
| Nationality         | russian        | german |
| Pet         | frog          | goat     |
| Sport   | climbing        | basketball     |

 